en-US.title: Birch Grove Health Center - Transgender Health Services
en-US.description: Birch Grove Health Center, a La Clinica facility, offers comprehensive health services tailored to the needs of the transgender community. This includes inclusive family planning, mental health counseling, adult physicals including annual well-woman exams, and referrals to specialty care. With a commitment to affordable excellence for all, Birch Grove ensures accessibility to health services for transmasculine, transfeminine, and non-binary individuals.

address: 910 S Central Ave, Medford, OR 97501, USA
